{"tid":1973881,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"［滲透］其實班「白警」應該成立工會，團結起黎","createTime":"2020-04-15T13:01:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-15T13:48:58.000Z","uid":35870,"like":3,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"7aa13862e678010d9fe2c20dc6b9082839580301","tid":1973881,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T13:01:08.000Z","msg":"中二病ff:<br />\n<br />\n1）首先，連登應該無人否認滲透的作用。不過，好多人會質疑，投考警隊後，入左警隊嘅人，會好易變質，就好似一大班14年雨傘革命後的人入左警隊後，變得奶共。<br />\n<br />\n2）我個人認為主因在於「白警」係狗隊入面勢孤力弱，群眾壓力下，根本無可能堅持自己嘅信念。所以白警要做嘅：係團結。<br />\n<br />\n3）「白警」應該主動聯繫有公信力嘅深黃組織（eg. Gphone眾志)，由組織去聯繫各人，或者由gphone endorsement 底下，成立有公信力嘅白警工會組織。長遠建立起近似於當年中國革命黨係各軍隊嘅政治勢力。<br />\n<br />\n4）要做「白警」，當然要「投名狀」，方法一，係公開自己係「白警」，同老細同同事對抗，擺到明做又36，唔做又36，拎住份糧吹得我脹；方法二，以近乎臥底角色潛伏，收集黑警罪狀，做二五仔。<br />\n<br />\n5）於是，「白警」工會分成三類運作，一類係公開左自己係白警，公然對抗老細嘅領袖角色；一類係唔公開嘅二五仔，收集罪證，出賣隊友（老豆搵仔得到咁多黑警資訊我認為方法類似）；仲有一類係有公信力嘅深黃人物，作為中間人聯繫大家（近似於同盟會宋教仁一類嘅角色）<br />\n<br />\n6）至於一般平民大眾，繼續鄙視、杯葛、排斥所有「黑警」及其家人。除非佢明確咁公開自己係白警，積極對抗，如果唔係，一律當做黑警，就算你自稱臥底都係咁話。臥底就係臥底，做臥底就係要眾叛親離，防止任何扮臥底可能性。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPs:不鼓吹任何犯法行為，以上純屬工會宣傳。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16bcdbe6d4b118a3e8e58af7294d76b41b51503f","tid":1973881,"uid":60527,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T13:04:34.000Z","msg":"警察唔可以組工會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41f5f6b67ffe904f39665df75fa2a67d7dc08e2b","tid":1973881,"uid":125168,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T13:05:00.000Z","msg":"公開自己係「白警」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你打個陣有無笑"},{"pid":"8a9d85a2dd30f2778da1c01eb2d6148855c86e0b","tid":1973881,"uid":244451,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T13:05:46.000Z","msg":"個肺白啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b08602dc83fa00e44e3e89d2afffe0b5f08a0d49","tid":1973881,"uid":125168,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T13:05:55.000Z","msg":"方法二，以近乎臥底角色潛伏，收集黑警罪狀，做二五仔。<br />\n<br />\n白警本身就應該係咁，但我哋都係當全部警察係敵人"},{"pid":"234d6694f49cc25328466b8703a347de103faadb","tid":1973881,"uid":318505,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T13:06:00.000Z","msg":"首先個會長可能會變成徐步高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d22c20f444135f717c9c5e69b8273d123252259f","tid":1973881,"uid":108359,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T13:07:36.000Z","msg":"成立police secrets先"},{"pid":"a346dac3b88b4528e8131e60621063ebb27d0e65","tid":1973881,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"16bcdbe6d4b118a3e8e58af7294d76b41b51503f","tid":1973881,"uid":60527,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T13:04:34.000Z","msg":"警察唔可以組工會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T13:08:47.000Z","msg":"呀sorry<br />\n啱先查返，原來犯法<br />\n我修正，係成立「興趣協會」"},{"pid":"02dc13fe09cf0f484f46c09d22addf84f1d00a82","tid":1973881,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d22c20f444135f717c9c5e69b8273d123252259f","tid":1973881,"uid":108359,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T13:07:36.000Z","msg":"成立police secrets先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T13:09:14.000Z","msg":"Facebook secret?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e736a533d06262f00a687204b3bafdb07732f2d","tid":1973881,"uid":342786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"41f5f6b67ffe904f39665df75fa2a67d7dc08e2b","tid":1973881,"uid":125168,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T13:05:00.000Z","msg":"公開自己係「白警」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkg